        "start": 21,
        "end": 23
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_010_000017",
    "sentence": "乙未，有司言：「乘輿車、牛馬、禽獸皆非禮，不宜以葬。」奏可。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_010_000018",
    "sentence": "七月，大赦天下。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_010_000019",
    "sentence": "建始元年 春正月乙丑，皇曾祖悼考廟災。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_010_000020",
    "sentence": "立故河間王弟上郡庫令良爲王。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "故河間王弟上郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 1,
        "end": 8
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_010_000021",
    "sentence": "有星孛于營室。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_010_000022",
    "sentence": "罷上林詔獄。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_010_000023",
    "sentence": "二月，右將軍長史姚尹等使匈奴還，去塞百餘里，暴風火發，燒殺尹等七人。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "將軍",
